        "id": 1116294
      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-03-15T15:26:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "iOS calls dumpWithoutCrash in our freeze detection logic.  We def do not want to upload immediately when the app is expected to be frozen.\n\nDo you feel strongly about this?  We could add a boolean that says something like generate_minidump_immediately?",
      "parentUuid": "cc7bf15a_f52c87d7",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 90,
        "startChar": 46,
        "endLine": 91,
